README.txt
Habit Tracker Web Application (Flask)

1. Overview

This project is a Habit Tracking Web Application built using:

Flask (Python backend)

HTML / Jinja2 (templating)

CSS (custom UI design)

JavaScript (Chart.js for analytics and UI interactions)

The application allows users to register, log in, manage habits, maintain streaks, track long-term goals, and view analytical charts.

2. Features
   2.1 User Authentication

Secure login and registration

Password visibility toggle

Form validation

Session-based authentication

2.2 Habit Management

Add, edit, and delete habits

Daily completion checkboxes

Auto-submit on click

Streak counter with animated bar

Tooltip for last completed date

2.3 Goal Management

Create long-term goals

Edit and delete goals

Automatic progress percentage

Styled progress bars

2.4 Analytics Dashboard

Habit completion line chart (Chart.js)

Goal progress bar chart (Chart.js)

Data dynamically passed through Flask using JSON

2.5 Responsive Layout

Mobile-friendly navigation

Flexible cards and container layouts

Media queries for smaller screen sizes

